   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Tiran s te numesc<text:line-break/> Nici nu voiu, nici nu-ndrsnesc.<text:line-break/> De vreme ce mie-m placi,<text:line-break/> i cu moartea care-mi faci.<text:line-break/> Atta numai i zic,<text:line-break/> S n-o numeri drept nimic.<text:line-break/> i drept bgtela chiar,<text:line-break/> A m omor-n zadar.<text:line-break/> Ca s nu-i fie vrun cias,<text:line-break/> Pentru cte trag -am tras.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> S vezi nete rspltiri,<text:line-break/> i singur s te miri.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cum nu socoteti vr-o dat</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cum nu socoteti vr-o dat<text:line-break/> C eti i judecat.<text:line-break/> Carea-n treab p ori cine,<text:line-break/> De a fcut ru, sau bine.<text:line-break/> i gndind la rspltire,<text:line-break/> S-i vii singur-n simire.<text:line-break/> i s lai atta rele,<text:line-break/> Care faci inimii mele,<text:line-break/> De gndeti c n-o s-i vie,<text:line-break/> Cte mi le faci tu mie,<text:line-break/> Vei vedea vr-o dinioar<text:line-break/> Ct de mult o s te doar,<text:line-break/> Ale mele toate zise,<text:line-break/> Ce le numeri tot drept vise,<text:line-break/> i drept basne aa nume,<text:line-break/> Ai greal, las glume,<text:line-break/> i nelege, te deteapt,<text:line-break/> C judecata t-ateapt,<text:line-break/> Unde n-or s fie jocuri,<text:line-break/> Cte-mi dai dureri i focuri,<text:line-break/> Vrei s dai rspuns la toate,<text:line-break/> Cte una cnd l-oi scoate,<text:line-break/> Artnd din ce pricin,<text:line-break/> Mai cznit ne avnd vin,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> De aceia de-e team,<text:line-break/> De dreptate bag seam,<text:line-break/> Nu vrsa n zadar snge<text:line-break/> Ce atunci te poate plnge,<text:line-break/> Ci i vin-o n simire<text:line-break/> i cunoate c din fire,<text:line-break/> Nu poi face strmbtate<text:line-break/> Unde vezi numai dreptate.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">i art cu jurmnt</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">i art cu jurmnt<text:line-break/> C a nu sta la cuvnt,<text:line-break/> -a strica paroala dat<text:line-break/> Nu te credeam nici odat,<text:line-break/> Tot deauna socoteam<text:line-break/> i a crede m sileam,<text:line-break/> C poi fi deosebit<text:line-break/> i la cei voii robit,<text:line-break/> Iar acuma pe dintreg<text:line-break/> ncepui s neleg,<text:line-break/> C la cte mi vei spune<text:line-break/> Nici un temeiu nu pociu pune.<text:line-break/> Cnd mi zici c m iubeti<text:line-break/> Te leini, te prpdeti,<text:line-break/> Cnd te vz iar cu schimbare<text:line-break/> i deosebire mare,<text:line-break/> Apoi nici aci nu stai<text:line-break/> i tot pricin mi dai,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> i te ari cu durere<text:line-break/> Mai cernd ntemeere,<text:line-break/> Nu tiu i eu ce s zic<text:line-break/> C or ce voiu face stric,<text:line-break/> Cum voiu gndi am greal<text:line-break/> Cci dragostea m nal,<text:line-break/> Nici ntr-un fel nu te-apuc<text:line-break/> C eti chiar ca un nluc,<text:line-break/> i asemenea ca luna<text:line-break/> Ce s schimb totdauna,<text:line-break/> Ci dar m rog s m eri<text:line-break/> De vreme ce-n do pri<text:line-break/> i s-nduplec cuvntul<text:line-break/> Dincotro i bate vntul.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ochiori frumoi</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Ochiori frumoi<text:line-break/> Dulci i mngiui,<text:line-break/> Ce stai mnioi?<text:line-break/> Voi v bucurai,<text:line-break/> Cnd m-ntmpinai.<text:line-break/> Iar nu v-ntristai,<text:line-break/> V tiam pornii,<text:line-break/> S m miluii<text:line-break/> Voi m chinuii.<text:line-break/> -acum m pricep<text:line-break/> C st la gazep,<text:line-break/> Nu tiu ce s-ncep.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> C s v-nblnzesc,<text:line-break/> Cci m tot sfiesc,<text:line-break/> S v necjesc.<text:line-break/> Vinovat nu sunt,<text:line-break/> V fac jurmnt,<text:line-break/> i cu ce cuvnt?<text:line-break/> S v necjii<text:line-break/> i s urgisii,<text:line-break/> P un cel robii.<text:line-break/> De sunt vinovat,<text:line-break/> Spunei-mi curat?<text:line-break/> S tiu-devrat.<text:line-break/> Ce fel s urmezu,<text:line-break/> S v-ncredinezu,<text:line-break/> i cum s-ndreptezu.<text:line-break/> Ochiori cu haz,<text:line-break/> Lsa-i acest tarz,<text:line-break/> Cci de mult m arz.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cu lanurile ce le-ntinzi</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cu lanurile ce le-tinzi,<text:line-break/> Din ai ti ochi rnitori?<text:line-break/> tiu bine c inimi prinzi,<text:line-break/> Nu pasri privigtori.<text:line-break/> i-nc-ai dup ce le prinzi,<text:line-break/> De ce nu le i omori,<text:line-break/> Ci numai vei s le prinzi,<text:line-break/> Cias p cias de mii de ori.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> De arzi pn le deprinzi<text:line-break/> Cu flacr, de faci haz,<text:line-break/> Apoi de-am le desprinzi<text:line-break/> Pentru mai mare necaz,<text:line-break/> nct te faci c desprinzi<text:line-break/> Cum i mrejile le uii<text:line-break/> i c aprinzi ct coprinzi<text:line-break/> Cu ochi-ncotro te uii.<text:line-break/> Acestea de ni le vinzi<text:line-break/> Drept marghioli te-amageti<text:line-break/> Minilor ce sunt oglinzi,<text:line-break/> C vd curat ce gndeti</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cine are piept s poarte</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cine are piept s poarte?<text:line-break/> Focuri i dureri de moarte<text:line-break/> i s fie odihnit,<text:line-break/> Suferind cu mulmit<text:line-break/> Aa patim cumplit<text:line-break/> Fr d-as-arta mhnit.<text:line-break/> Numai eu m vz n stare<text:line-break/> C m arz fr-de-ntristare<text:line-break/> i rznd s m topesc.<text:line-break/> Numrnd drept datorie<text:line-break/> A muri cu bucurie<text:line-break/> Pentr-aceia ci-o iubesc.<text:line-break/> Muli gndesc c desprire<text:line-break/> N-am din cei fr simire<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Piatr zic c sunt i fier.<text:line-break/> Vznd ast fel de rbdare<text:line-break/> Fr-d-avea asmnare<text:line-break/> i s mir cum nu pier.<text:line-break/> Mcar c au i dreptate<text:line-break/> De urmri aa ciudate<text:line-break/> Toi de obta s mira.<text:line-break/> S am moarte drept plcere<text:line-break/> i s sufer cu durere<text:line-break/> Fr-de-a nu m supra.<text:line-break/> Dar greesc, c n-au tiin<text:line-break/> C cu poft i voin<text:line-break/> A rbda este dator.<text:line-break/> Cine e s te-nleag?<text:line-break/> i o mucenie-ntreag,<text:line-break/> Nu c e nesimitor.<text:line-break/> De aceia, cu-ntregime,<text:line-break/> De simiri, nu cu prostime,<text:line-break/> C ct eti nelegnd.<text:line-break/> -al meu suflet te iubete,<text:line-break/> i de voe s trudete,<text:line-break/> i s bucur arznd.<text:line-break/> Dar m rog de nelege,<text:line-break/> C la pieptu meu e lege,<text:line-break/> Pentru tine a ofta.<text:line-break/> -a rbda dureri i chinuri,<text:line-break/> Patimi, focuri, i suspinuri,<text:line-break/> i a nu s veta.<text:line-break/> i rmi ncredinat,<text:line-break/> C d-oi muri vro dat,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Tot acelai fiind eu.<text:line-break/> C i-n iad i fite unde,<text:line-break/> Voi striga fr de ascunde,<text:line-break/> C tu eti amorul meu.(42)pag.<text:line-break/> Chiar de nu m crezi pe mine,<text:line-break/> ntreab i p ori cine.<text:line-break/> i vezi cte ptimete,<text:line-break/> Un suflet ce te iubete.<text:line-break/> ntreab dar i p lume,<text:line-break/> i s vezi c nu sunt glume.<text:line-break/> C necazurile mele,<text:line-break/> Carele petrec cu ele,<text:line-break/> De lacrmi vars prae,<text:line-break/> Cu o groaznic vpae.<text:line-break/> Ct i sufleelu-mi este,<text:line-break/> De ohtturi multe dese.<text:line-break/> i un cias nu vz odihn,<text:line-break/> Ca s dorm vreodat-n ticn.<text:line-break/> Durerile mi sunt hran,<text:line-break/> i mngere la ran.<text:line-break/> M arde fr de msur,<text:line-break/> i slbesc fr de cldur.<text:line-break/> C sunt bolnav din picere,<text:line-break/> i murind o fac tcere.<text:line-break/> Cnd nu te vz le am chinuri<text:line-break/> i cnd te zresc leinuri,</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Hain eti la toate</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Hain eti la toate<text:line-break/> La cte te-am rugat,<text:line-break/> mi zici c nu se poate<text:line-break/> M mir ce -am stricat,<text:line-break/> Rpui cu a ta fire<text:line-break/> Fr milostivire<text:line-break/> Viee Omeneti,<text:line-break/> Izvor eti plin de haruri<text:line-break/> Dar ai -aceste daruri<text:line-break/> Faci haz s pedepseti,<text:line-break/> Suspinurile mele<text:line-break/> i desele ohtri<text:line-break/> Vei s le ai pre ele<text:line-break/> Ca nite desftri,<text:line-break/> Te bucuri dumnete<text:line-break/> De cel ce te iubete<text:line-break/> Vzndu-l ntristat,<text:line-break/> A cruia-ntristare<text:line-break/> Va s t-aduc-n stare<text:line-break/> S plngi ne ncetat,<text:line-break/> Cci carele rnete<text:line-break/> Al altuia amar<text:line-break/> Pcatul l gonete<text:line-break/> D-ai fi rvna-n zadar,<text:line-break/> Ia-i seam dar vezi bine<text:line-break/> C nu i s cuvine<text:line-break/> Cumplit s pedepseti,<text:line-break/> Prea cela ce-i arat,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> i dragostea i fapt<text:line-break/> Prea cela s-l iubeti.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Suflet hain nu-i pcat?</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Suflet hain nu-i pcat?<text:line-break/> S m vezi tot nfocat,<text:line-break/> i dintru adnc ohtnd,<text:line-break/> n chinuri petrecnd.<text:line-break/> Ajung ct mai trudit,<text:line-break/> C doar de-ai fi mulmit,<text:line-break/> A m vedea ptimind,<text:line-break/> i cu necazuri trind.<text:line-break/> Fericire n-am avut,<text:line-break/> Din ciasul ce te-am vzut,<text:line-break/> Ce pururea-nprotiviri,<text:line-break/> Suspinuri i tnguiri.<text:line-break/> Tocmai ca o pervenea,<text:line-break/> S arde inima mea<text:line-break/> i nu are rezmnt,<text:line-break/> La nimenea pre pmnt.<text:line-break/> Am hotrt i voesc<text:line-break/> Ct voiu avea s tresc<text:line-break/> Pe alt chip s nu iubesc<text:line-break/> De ct pe care-l slvesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Cu inima aprins</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cu inima aprins<text:line-break/> n flacr nestins,<text:line-break/> Zioa noaptea ohtez.<text:line-break/> Am spune chin prea,<text:line-break/> Dorul i tnguirea,<text:line-break/> La nimeni nu cutez.<text:line-break/> Ticlosul de mine,<text:line-break/> Cte o dat-m vine,<text:line-break/> S viu ie s-spun.<text:line-break/> Inima m oprete,<text:line-break/> M ine, m sfiete,<text:line-break/> i d-aceia rpuiu.<text:line-break/> Numai prin mijlocire,<text:line-break/> Cnd avem ntlnire,<text:line-break/> Cumva s te zresc.<text:line-break/> Chinurile m las<text:line-break/> Nicierea nu-m pas<text:line-break/> Focul m rcoresc.<text:line-break/> Apoi fr de vrere<text:line-break/> Cnd te perz din vedere<text:line-break/> Mai cumplit ptimesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pna cnd nu te iubeam</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Pna cnd nu te iubeam<text:line-break/> Unde m culcam dormeam.<text:line-break/> Acum de cnd te iubesc<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Nu pociu s m odihnesc.<text:line-break/> Rpuiu m sfresc de dor<text:line-break/> Fr nici un ajutor.<text:line-break/> Arz m frig n mare foc<text:line-break/> N-am astmpr la un loc.<text:line-break/> Suflet nu me-a mai rmas<text:line-break/> Ohtnd mii de ori p cias.<text:line-break/> Cu totul m-am prpdit<text:line-break/> Minile mi s-a zmintit.<text:line-break/> Es din cas m duc,<text:line-break/> Nu tiu ncotro s-apuc.<text:line-break/> Viu iar m ntorc i ez<text:line-break/> Stau n loc i suspinez.<text:line-break/> Inima mea vai de ia<text:line-break/> De la tin-nu s mai ia</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pna cnd eti la stat</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Minunat eti la stat<text:line-break/> i nostim la umblat.<text:line-break/> Ai doi ochiori frumoi<text:line-break/> Blnzi cu totul mngioi.<text:line-break/> Rnind cu privirea lor<text:line-break/> Inimile tuturor.<text:line-break/> Iscusit, i cu haz<text:line-break/> De suppui or ce obraz<text:line-break/> Omori inimi tari p loc.<text:line-break/> i le aprinzi cu greu foc.<text:line-break/> Rpind simiri tinereti<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> i fermeci, i i uimeti.<text:line-break/> Aprinzndu-i cu amor<text:line-break/> i de tine s omor.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Pn cnd un soare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Razele de la un soare<text:line-break/> Cele prea strlucitoare,<text:line-break/> n faa ta lumineaz<text:line-break/> Ct firea s minuneaz.<text:line-break/> Ai ochi frumoi peste fire<text:line-break/> npodobii cu simire<text:line-break/> Care cu a lor privire<text:line-break/> Aduc minilor uimire.<text:line-break/> La trup eti ndelecat<text:line-break/> Potrivit minunat<text:line-break/> nct cin te zrete<text:line-break/> De o dat s rnete.<text:line-break/> Un eti tu ntre toate<text:line-break/> Asemeneai nu s poate<text:line-break/> Cu totul npodobit<text:line-break/> Tocmai ca o afrodit.<text:line-break/> Uit-te cu mil puic<text:line-break/> Nu trece ca o nluc.<text:line-break/> ine-i ochiorii bine<text:line-break/> i te uit drept la mine.<text:line-break/> Inima mi-o tii prea bine.<text:line-break/> Nu trebue d-ai mai spune.<text:line-break/> Caut fii miostiv,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Cum urma tot n grotiv.<text:line-break/> Ogrvindu-m n fa<text:line-break/> S-m scurtezi a mea via.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Tineree frumusee</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Tineree<text:line-break/> Frumusee<text:line-break/> -alte daruri cte sunt.<text:line-break/> Isteciune<text:line-break/> Nelepciune<text:line-break/> La tine-s ntr-un cuvnt.<text:line-break/> Numai un<text:line-break/> Te cunun<text:line-break/> Firea toat pre pmnt.<text:line-break/> Cci or care<text:line-break/> Spre n-dreptare<text:line-break/> Te-arat cu jurmnt.<text:line-break/> Alt fire<text:line-break/> Cu-mplinire<text:line-break/> A fi nu-i de crezmnt,<text:line-break/> Afrodit,<text:line-break/> ntocmit<text:line-break/> Eti fr de sczmnt.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Jurmnt l-a mea iubit</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Jurmnt l-a mea iubit<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Fcusem stranic, i sfnt,<text:line-break/> S-o iubesc ne osebit<text:line-break/> n pieptu-mi s-o am slvit.<text:line-break/> Pn voiu intra n pmnt,<text:line-break/> O acest fel dar fini<text:line-break/> Legtur de amor<text:line-break/> Am scris-o p-o frunzuli,<text:line-break/> D-un pom ntr-o grdini<text:line-break/> Verde, pentru vecinic dor.<text:line-break/> Ivindu-s ns-ndat<text:line-break/> Iute mnios un vnt<text:line-break/> Frunzulia fu suflat,<text:line-break/> i n aer deprtat<text:line-break/> N-a mai rmas jurmnt.<text:line-break/> intuit ntru-ntristare<text:line-break/> Am rugat-o lcrmnd<text:line-break/> S mai aib adstare,<text:line-break/> Poate iari vr-un vnt mare<text:line-break/> m va da frunza curnd.<text:line-break/> Adio i-am zis fini<text:line-break/> i pieptul meu o ohtat<text:line-break/> Adio i-am zis zei,<text:line-break/> i srutnd-on guri<text:line-break/> De dnsa m-am deprtat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Osebire amar</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Osebire amar<text:line-break/> Osebire ria,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Osebire cu par<text:line-break/> Osebire gria.<text:line-break/> Toat lumea-m pare<text:line-break/> Iad ntunecat,<text:line-break/> -a ei luminare<text:line-break/> N negru nbrcat.<text:line-break/> N-are cum nimic<text:line-break/> N ia de fericit,<text:line-break/> Dac i-am rdic<text:line-break/> A tu chip strlucit.<text:line-break/> Iar cu ntmplare<text:line-break/> Cnd te dobndesc,<text:line-break/> A le ei amare<text:line-break/> Nu le socotesc.<text:line-break/> Amor i rnire<text:line-break/> N mine s unesc,<text:line-break/> Munci i chinuire<text:line-break/> Ndat m gsesc.<text:line-break/> La toate aceste<text:line-break/> mpotriva- sta<text:line-break/> Dar mai grea m este<text:line-break/> Osebirea ta.<text:line-break/> Pieptu-m ticlosul<text:line-break/> Fr s-l doreti,<text:line-break/> Prea ne norocosul<text:line-break/> Tot l pedepseti.<text:line-break/> -a ta osebire<text:line-break/> N-are ne greit<text:line-break/> Fr prelungire<text:line-break/> Oi s-m de-a sfrit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Gndesc s plec s m duc</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Gndesc s plec s m duc,<text:line-break/> Iar de un dor m usuc.<text:line-break/> i m cuprinde o jale,<text:line-break/> C m deprtez n cale.<text:line-break/> C d-un puiu m despresc,<text:line-break/> Poate nu-l mai ntlnesc.<text:line-break/> Care m-a iubit cu mil,<text:line-break/> Ne fcndu-i nici o sil.<text:line-break/> N-am ce face plng! ohtez,<text:line-break/> Cu greu foc m deprtez.<text:line-break/> Ci m rog cu lacrmi multe,<text:line-break/> Ca dragostea s nu-m uite.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cum plec de la dumneata</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cum plec de la dumneata,<text:line-break/> P loc ncep a ohta.<text:line-break/> i nu tiu-ncotro s-apuc,<text:line-break/> Nu tiu unde s m duc.<text:line-break/> M mir ce dor urgisit,<text:line-break/> Pentru tine m-a gsit.<text:line-break/> De nu poci nici un minut,<text:line-break/> Din gndul meu s te uit.<text:line-break/> Un cias de nu te-oi vedea,<text:line-break/> Nu-m vine-n loc d-a edea.<text:line-break/> De-m pare c-n nebunesc,<text:line-break/> Pn cnd te ntlnesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Tot de dor, de dor, de dor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Tot de dor, de dor, de dor,<text:line-break/> Tot de dor vz c-oi s mor,<text:line-break/> Tot de dorul unui ce,<text:line-break/> Nu pociu spune pentru ce.<text:line-break/> Oi s mor s m sfresc,<text:line-break/> i un tainic nu gsesc,<text:line-break/> Paraponul ca s-m spuiu,<text:line-break/> i focul s mi-l rapuiu,<text:line-break/> C d-a spune alt cuiva<text:line-break/> M tem s nu-l fac vrjma,<text:line-break/> i-n loc s m folosesc,<text:line-break/> Voi fi-n veac s m cesc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cine ptimete cine</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cine ptimete cine?<text:line-break/> Aa de cumplit ca mine,<text:line-break/> Vie, vie s m vaz,<text:line-break/> Vaz, vaz i s-m creaz,<text:line-break/> Ah! ah! ah! cine m vede,<text:line-break/> Vede ,vede i nu crede,<text:line-break/> Cu ce foc petrec n lume,<text:line-break/> Numai eu tiu i un nume,<text:line-break/> Care i el ptimete,<text:line-break/> Ca mine s pedepsete,<text:line-break/> Acela care mi crede,<text:line-break/> Acela cu dor m vede.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Spune inimioar spune</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Spune inimioar spune<text:line-break/> Ce durere te rpune?<text:line-break/> Iart ce te muncete,<text:line-break/> Ce boal te chinuete?<text:line-break/> F-o cunoscut mie,<text:line-break/> Ca s-i caut dohtorie?<text:line-break/> Te rog f-m d-a pricepe,<text:line-break/> Boala din ce i s-ncepe?<text:line-break/> D-m un cuvnt i-m rspunde,<text:line-break/> Arat spune n-ascunde?<text:line-break/> D-m un cuvnt i-m rspunde<text:line-break/> Spune inimioar spune?<text:line-break/> Ce durere te rpune.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vai de doi ce s iubesc</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Vai de doi ce s iubesc<text:line-break/> -ntre ei cnd nu-ndrznesc,<text:line-break/> Inimile  sgiat<text:line-break/> i dragostea nu- arat.<text:line-break/> Amndoi ard ntr-un foc<text:line-break/> N-au astmpr la un loc,<text:line-break/> Umbl uimii nu s-aaz<text:line-break/> Tot doresc ca s se vaz,<text:line-break/> Aa -eu fiind rnit<text:line-break/> Umblu tot ne odihnit,<text:line-break/> C amorul e foc mare<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Dac n-are-ncredinare</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Dragostea, fohul, de dor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Dragostea, fohul, de dor,<text:line-break/> Omoar pre om cu zor.<text:line-break/> C de suspin i ohtat,<text:line-break/> Te-arunc de zaci n pat.<text:line-break/> Vai amar! amar! amar!<text:line-break/> Ia vezi mil ia vezi dor,<text:line-break/> Ce ctigi de la amor?<text:line-break/> C-n loc s te foloseti,<text:line-break/> Cu patim te pomeneti.<text:line-break/> Vai amar!...<text:line-break/> C n dreptate nu in,<text:line-break/> Nici mcar ct de puin.<text:line-break/> Dac st la interes,<text:line-break/> La ce eu din mini s-m es?<text:line-break/> Vai amar!amar!amar!</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Vezi cu ochii i nu-m crezi</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Vezi cu ochii, i nu-m crezi,<text:line-break/> i m-ntrebi? De ce ohtezi.<text:line-break/> Ohtez sufleelul meu,<text:line-break/> C foarte m pas greu.<text:line-break/> Oi s mor de ah! i vai!<text:line-break/> i dumneata tire n-ai.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> C dorul m-a ohticat,<text:line-break/> i suspinul m-a secat.<text:line-break/> M mir cum de nu gndeti,<text:line-break/> C sunt rspltiri fireti.<text:line-break/> De s-n torc mai cu prisos,<text:line-break/> Ctr cel necredincios.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Oi s mor, ah oi s mor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Oi s mor, ah oi s mor<text:line-break/> Amrt, i plin de dor.<text:line-break/> Nu tiu scris,nu tiu fcut,<text:line-break/> Vz, c parte n-am avut.<text:line-break/> Oi s mor,ah! oi s mor,<text:line-break/> Fr nici un ajutor.<text:line-break/> N-am p nimini niciri,<text:line-break/> S-m dea ranii lecuiri.<text:line-break/> Vedei traiu ru i trudit,<text:line-break/> Amrt i dosdit.<text:line-break/> Numai unii cu noroc,<text:line-break/> i alii s ard n foc.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">M topesc eu pentru tine</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">M topesc eu pentru tine,<text:line-break/> i nu- e mil de mine.<text:line-break/> Nu tiu pentru care sil,<text:line-break/> Mai urt fr de mil.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> C eu prea mult n credin<text:line-break/> Te-am iubit tot cu dorin.<text:line-break/> Poi s ei pliroforie,<text:line-break/> Faa mea spre mrturie.<text:line-break/> Ah! ajung dar, ajung,<text:line-break/> Atta mnie lung.<text:line-break/> C e pcat pentru mine,<text:line-break/> Dar e ru i pentru tine.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Bat-l Dumnezeu d-amor</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Bat-l Dumnezeu d-amor,<text:line-break/> C m-a prpdit de dor.<text:line-break/> Zio, nopte, m muncete,<text:line-break/> Trupul ru m chinuete.<text:line-break/> Bat-l Dumnezeu d-amor,<text:line-break/> C m-a prpdit de dor.<text:line-break/> Nici un minut nu-m d pace<text:line-break/> N toat vremea n-am cei face.<text:line-break/> Bat-l Dumnezeu d-amor<text:line-break/> C m-a prpdit de dor,<text:line-break/> M usuc, m slbete,<text:line-break/> Viaa m ticloete.<text:line-break/> Bat-l Dumnezeu d-amor,<text:line-break/> C m-a prpdit de dor<text:line-break/> Umblu tot ntr-o uimire<text:line-break/> Pare c nu-m sunt n fire.<text:line-break/> Bat-l Dumnezu d-amor,<text:line-break/> C m-a prpdit de dor<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> i-m fcu ponos n lume,<text:line-break/> C m-nchin lui, pentru un nume.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ah! o psric</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Ah! o psric,<text:line-break/> Mult odihna-m stric.<text:line-break/> Tot pricin-m face,<text:line-break/> Nu m las-n pace.<text:line-break/> Nu tiu ce gnd are,<text:line-break/> Asta ei urmare,<text:line-break/> C prea m arat,<text:line-break/> Fa-namorat,<text:line-break/> Ivindu-s vine,<text:line-break/> Aprope de mine,<text:line-break/> i m ciripete,<text:line-break/> De m-n nebunete.<text:line-break/> Cnd s-o arunc zboar,<text:line-break/> Cnd stau s scoboar,<text:line-break/> Nici va s se duc,<text:line-break/> Nici nu s apuc.<text:line-break/> Ast psric,<text:line-break/> Ce linitea-m stric,<text:line-break/> Altfel nu s prinde,<text:line-break/> Dect la d-ai tinde.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Aluni lumintoare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Aluni lumintoare,<text:line-break/> i stele strlucitoare.<text:line-break/> Luminai mai cu trie,<text:line-break/> Scumpa mea cltorie.<text:line-break/> Dai lumin nfocat,<text:line-break/> Pn crarea-ntunecat.<text:line-break/> S vz drumul d-a m duce,<text:line-break/> La iubita mea cea dulce.<text:line-break/> Carea trist i deteapt,<text:line-break/> Cu dor mare m ateapt.<text:line-break/> Ca s ajung ct mai tare,<text:line-break/> S-m dea dulce srutare.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Munilor fii mrturii</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Munilor fii mrturii<text:line-break/> C prin voi cltorii.<text:line-break/> Cu sufletul plin de dor,<text:line-break/> -ichima de dogor.<text:line-break/> Pduri copaci nfrunzii<text:line-break/> i voi mrturii s-m fii.<text:line-break/> Cu ce chin i cu ce foc,<text:line-break/> Am trecut prin acest loc.<text:line-break/> Ruri, ape mari i mici,<text:line-break/> Ce v-am trecut pn aici.<text:line-break/> Nu uitai cu ce nevoi!<text:line-break/> Am but ap din voi.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Mierlie, privigtori,<text:line-break/> Psri dulci glsuitori.<text:line-break/> Cntai i voi acest vers,<text:line-break/> La truditului meu mers.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Azi, rz, vorbesc i glumesc</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Azi rz, vorbesc i glumesc,<text:line-break/> Cu ceia ce o iubesc.<text:line-break/> -amndoi ne mngem,<text:line-break/> Foc i dor numai avem.<text:line-break/> Azi soarele-a luminat,<text:line-break/> Mai frumos, mai seninat.<text:line-break/> C ceia ce doream,<text:line-break/> Acum cu mine o am.<text:line-break/> Azi luna a strlucit,<text:line-break/> Limpede mai ndulcit.<text:line-break/> C ceia ce-am gndit,<text:line-break/> Acum o am dobndit.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cum ziceai c m iubeti</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cum ziceai c m iubeti,<text:line-break/> Nu gndeam s m ureti.<text:line-break/> -att s m deprtezi,<text:line-break/> Ct nu vei nici s m vezi<text:line-break/> M mir cum te-ai ndurat,<text:line-break/> D-al meu dor nflcrat.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Aa ru de te-ai scrbit,<text:line-break/> i att te-ai osebit.<text:line-break/> Dragostea ci-o artai,<text:line-break/> i ndejdea ce mi-o dai.<text:line-break/> I-am veac n-a fi socotit,<text:line-break/> S fiu aa oropsit.<text:line-break/> Ah! cerule-n nalt i sfnt,<text:line-break/> Tinde-i mila pre pmnt.<text:line-break/> i-m d al tu ajutor,<text:line-break/> Ca un drept judector.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">O! Iubita mea ce dulce</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">O! Iubita mea cea dulce<text:line-break/> Sti nu fuci, nu te duce.<text:line-break/> Ateapt m rog fierbinte,<text:line-break/> S te ntreb doa cuvinte.<text:line-break/> Ce i-am greit? vin de-m spune,<text:line-break/> Nu grbi d-a m rpune.<text:line-break/> Or nu-i aduci aminte?<text:line-break/> D-ale tale jurminte,<text:line-break/> Cnd ziceai c pn la noapte,<text:line-break/> De min nu te vei desparte.<text:line-break/> Poate c nu eti cretin?<text:line-break/> De m ureti fr de vin.<text:line-break/> Du-te dar va veni vreme,<text:line-break/> De vei plnge, i vei geme<text:line-break/> Cnd te v-ajunge cu boal,<text:line-break/> A ta jurata paroal.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Stpna inimii mele</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Stpna inimii mele,<text:line-break/> i scump sufleelul meu,<text:line-break/> Tu simi i cunoti prea bine,<text:line-break/> Ct de mult te iubesc eu.<text:line-break/> Amorul ce m muncete,<text:line-break/> M silete s-i vorbesc,<text:line-break/> i s-i spuiu cu ndrzneal,<text:line-break/> C cu totul m robesc.<text:line-break/> Firea te-a fcut n lume,<text:line-break/> Cu un dor deosebit,<text:line-break/> C cum te-am vzut ndat,<text:line-break/> Din acel ceas te-am iubit.<text:line-break/> Tot dauna d-un foc mare,<text:line-break/> Peptul meu fiind ptruns,<text:line-break/> M-a fcut fr-ncetare,<text:line-break/> S suspinez ntr-ascuns.<text:line-break/> Inima mea cea rnit,<text:line-break/> Gndind s o tinuiesc,<text:line-break/> Dar nu a fost cu putin,<text:line-break/> C iar o destinuesc.<text:line-break/> Cu toate c nu-i lipsete,<text:line-break/> Aceste s i le spuiu,<text:line-break/> C faa m dovedete,<text:line-break/> n dorul care rpuiu.<text:line-break/> Ah! Ce mare bucurie,<text:line-break/> n mine a dobndi,<text:line-break/> Aciasta a mea iubire,<text:line-break/> De nu o vei osndi.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Sgei de dor arztoare</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Sgei de foc arztoare,<text:line-break/> Arunci din ochi cnd priveti,<text:line-break/> Rneti inimi simitoare,<text:line-break/> Or ncotro te iveti.<text:line-break/> Arcuri crunte, i ntinse,<text:line-break/> Din sprncene-nfiezi,<text:line-break/> De porneti focuri ne stinse,<text:line-break/> Aprinzi, suflet veninezi.<text:line-break/> Fiorii grele-nspimntate,<text:line-break/> Dai din buze cnd zmbeti,<text:line-break/> Ai junghiuri, ne curmate,<text:line-break/> Robeti, fermeci, mini uimeti,<text:line-break/> Tolbe pline narmate,<text:line-break/> Peste tot chipu tu pori,<text:line-break/> Ptrunzi piepturi de s bate,<text:line-break/> i rmi ca nite mori.<text:line-break/> Acest cntec i-l fac dare,<text:line-break/> i te rog s-l primeti,<text:line-break/> S-l ii pentru neuitare,<text:line-break/> n via ct treti.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Primvara cum sosete</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Primvara cum sosete<text:line-break/> Toat firea veselete,<text:line-break/> Pmntul tot nverzete,<text:line-break/> i de flori s-npodobete.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Cucul cnt rureaz<text:line-break/> Copacii n mugureaz,<text:line-break/> Dumbrvioar-nrmureaz,<text:line-break/> Vzduhul n semneaz.<text:line-break/> Pn grdini pn floricele,<text:line-break/> i pn pomi pn rmurele,<text:line-break/> Cnt privigtorele,<text:line-break/> i feluri de psrele.<text:line-break/> Toate prile rsun,<text:line-break/> Glasuri de prere bun,<text:line-break/> i tinerii flori adun,<text:line-break/> De  npletesc cunun.<text:line-break/> Nu mai eu de ntristare,<text:line-break/> Nici odat n-am scpare,<text:line-break/> Ci tot n chin, i dor mare,<text:line-break/> Ohtatul meu sfrit n-are.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Florile cum s ivesc</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Florile cum s ivesc,<text:line-break/> Psrilea-morizesc,<text:line-break/> Toate cu mare dogor,<text:line-break/> Una dup alta zbor.<text:line-break/> Apoi pn pomi cnd s pun,<text:line-break/> De viers zeferii rsun.<text:line-break/> i cu a lor zis firesc,<text:line-break/> Focurile- rsipesc.<text:line-break/> Ah! Cnd nite psrei,<text:line-break/> Tot au foc i dori i ei,<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Cu ct mai vrtos un om,<text:line-break/> Va putea s aib som.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cum sosete primvara</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cum sosete primvar,<text:line-break/> m d inim amar.<text:line-break/> Cci cnd m uit n grdin,<text:line-break/> Trupul meu n-are odin.<text:line-break/> Oriunde vz iarb verde,<text:line-break/> M-ntristeaz de m perde.<text:line-break/> Unde vz cte o floare,<text:line-break/> M rnete de m doare.<text:line-break/> Und-auz vro psric,<text:line-break/> Toat voia-mi s stric.<text:line-break/> C gndind me-aduc aminte,<text:line-break/> De cele mai din nainte.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Primvar timp frumos</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Primvar timp frumos,<text:line-break/> Mult eti bun i mngos.<text:line-break/> C tu ndat cum vii,<text:line-break/> Toat fptura n vii.<text:line-break/> Tu faci vzuhul senin,<text:line-break/> i la toi voia de plin.<text:line-break/> Tu pmntul veseleti,<text:line-break/> Cu iarb-l npodobeti.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Tu copacii nfrunzeti,<text:line-break/> i dumbrvile-nverzeti.<text:line-break/> Tu ne aduci floricei,<text:line-break/> i ne-nflorete geocei.<text:line-break/> -apoi cum pleci i te duci,<text:line-break/> Grdinile le usuci.<text:line-break/> Inimile la toi strici,<text:line-break/> De te jelesc mari i mici.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Primvar cum s-arat</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Primvar cum s-arat,<text:line-break/> n podobit-nflorat.<text:line-break/> Multe inimiori rnete,<text:line-break/> i spre amor le pornete.<text:line-break/> Cu dor mare le cuprinde,<text:line-break/> i cu foc greu le aprinde.<text:line-break/> Care alt leac numai are,<text:line-break/> Dect echisohi plimbare,<text:line-break/> Unii plec ru p vale,<text:line-break/> De s roresc n cale.<text:line-break/> Alii es la Olt s plimb,<text:line-break/> Vntui bate, doru- schimb.<text:line-break/> Uni la Inteti afar,<text:line-break/>  potolesc a lor par.<text:line-break/> i de vd c nu le trece,<text:line-break/> Beau i ct o ap rece.<text:line-break/> Alii p la cetue,<text:line-break/> Merg focul ca s-i rpue.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Precum s obicnuete,<text:line-break/> Fel de fel s rcorete.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Trecut-au primvar</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Trecut-au primvara,<text:line-break/> mbtnit-au vara,<text:line-break/> i iarna s- ivit.<text:line-break/> -acum cele-nflorite,<text:line-break/> Cu totul vetejite,<text:line-break/> Zpada le-a albit.<text:line-break/> Burienile uscar,<text:line-break/> i toate s plecar,<text:line-break/> Triste la pmnt.<text:line-break/> Frumuseea li s stinse,<text:line-break/> Pmntul le cuprinse,<text:line-break/> Parc nici nu sunt.<text:line-break/> Ia vezi dar tineree,<text:line-break/> n ce fel de bunee,<text:line-break/> Oi s te prefaci.<text:line-break/> i vrsta frgezit,<text:line-break/> Frumseea cea-nflorit,<text:line-break/> Aa oi s-o faci.<text:line-break/> Deci nu-i jindui viaa,<text:line-break/> Nici i popri dulceaa,<text:line-break/> n dor petrecnd.<text:line-break/> Ct n ast stare,<text:line-break/> Trete-n dezmerdare,<text:line-break/> Vreme neperznd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"><text:soft-page-break/></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Chitar muz-armoniceasc</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Chitar-muz-armoniceasc,<text:line-break/> Pn cnd oi s tcem?<text:line-break/> Pn cnd s ne munciasc,<text:line-break/> ntristarea ci-o avem.<text:line-break/> i cnd iari oi s-ncepem?<text:line-break/> Dulce s ne veselim,<text:line-break/> C din griji precum pricepem,<text:line-break/> Nimica nu folosim.<text:line-break/> Ciasul umblu, vremea trece,<text:line-break/> i noi nainte pim,<text:line-break/> Ne spune ne d jungiu rece,<text:line-break/> C vrsta ni-o moleim.<text:line-break/> i dac n ast floare,<text:line-break/> Cu dulcia nu trim,<text:line-break/> Cnd ndjdueti oare,<text:line-break/> Vrem ast s-o mai gsim.<text:line-break/> Duc-s doru-n tristarea,<text:line-break/> Duc-s, inima rea,<text:line-break/> Duc-s chinul,ohtarea,<text:line-break/> Duc-s grija cea grea.<text:line-break/> Iar noi cu o glsuire,<text:line-break/> Tot dauna s cntm,<text:line-break/> i tot cu bun voire,<text:line-break/> Slobozi s ne desftm.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Bine este totdaun</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Bine este tot daun,<text:line-break/> S bem s ne osptm,<text:line-break/> i cu toii din preun,<text:line-break/> S rdem i s cntm.<text:line-break/> Las lumea s vorbeasc,<text:line-break/> Strig, zbiere, ct o vrea,<text:line-break/> Gluma, jocul, s triasc,<text:line-break/> Voiu cu ea a m-ngropa.<text:line-break/> Venii frai s trim bine,<text:line-break/> Veselindu-ne-ntre noi,<text:line-break/> Cci prea curnd vremea vine,<text:line-break/> Cea-ncurcat cu nevoi.<text:line-break/> Ne apas ne-nconvoe,<text:line-break/> Cu mnia ei cea rea,<text:line-break/> i de jocuri ne despoe,<text:line-break/> Ne-nbrac cu hain grea.<text:line-break/> De btrni s ne ascundem,<text:line-break/> i s fugim ct putem,<text:line-break/> i necontenit s facem,<text:line-break/> Ce ne place i ce vrem.<text:line-break/> Nu voiu avere, nici bogie,<text:line-break/> Nu voiu mrire, nici avuie,<text:line-break/> Nu voiu simire, nu voesc minte,<text:line-break/> Nici isteciune, ct bob de linte.<text:line-break/> C-aceste toate, cin-le voete,<text:line-break/> Ct le-n mulete, s amrete<text:line-break/> Eu voesc pace i linite,<text:line-break/> Via bun, dulce iubire.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Voiu cntecele, desfttoare,<text:line-break/> Jocuri, i glume mngitoare.<text:line-break/> i cu aceste voiu totdaun.<text:line-break/> S mor cu ele stnd npreun.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">D-ar fi aurul ca s poat</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">D-ar fi aurul ca s poat,<text:line-break/> S-m dea via-ndelungat,<text:line-break/> Alt nimic n-a mai pofti;<text:line-break/> Ci m-a strdui d-a strnge,<text:line-break/> i de moarte nu m-a plnge,<text:line-break/> Cci l-am da i m-a plti.<text:line-break/> Dar de vreme ce nu poate,<text:line-break/> S m scoat de la moarte,<text:line-break/> D ce s m strduesc?<text:line-break/> Cu amar, i cu durere,<text:line-break/> Ca s dobndesc avere,<text:line-break/> La toi s m cciulesc.<text:line-break/> Mai bine srac n pace,<text:line-break/> S tresc cum mie-m place,<text:line-break/> Cci cnd va fi ca s mor.<text:line-break/> Petrecnd n srcie,<text:line-break/> Sfritul meu voiu s fie,<text:line-break/> ntre vii, -ntre amor.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>Noi fetele vizitate</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Noi fetele vizitate,<text:line-break/> Vrem s trim desftate.<text:line-break/> i s petrecem n lume,<text:line-break/> Tot cu rsuri, i cu glume.<text:line-break/> Noi iubim toate-n tot locul,<text:line-break/> Cntecele i jocul.<text:line-break/> Unde-s Oamenii buni la fire,<text:line-break/> i tresc n linitire.<text:line-break/> Noi cu ei vrem tot daun,<text:line-break/> S petrecem npreun.<text:line-break/> Unde-s cu firea ciudat,<text:line-break/> Nu vrem s fim nici odat.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Nimic nu-i ca vinu</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Nimic nu-i ca vinu,<text:line-break/> El ne d odinu.<text:line-break/> Lumea sfrit n-are,<text:line-break/> Cnd golim phare.<text:line-break/> Mhniri atunci n-avem,<text:line-break/> Cnd cntm i mult bem.<text:line-break/> Nici frica n-adap,<text:line-break/> Cnd nu bem pic de ap.<text:line-break/> Suge mi frtate,<text:line-break/> Ct ai sntate.<text:line-break/> C nu tim prea bine,<text:line-break/> Vii vom fi i mine.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/> Lic, lic,lic, lic,lic,lic.<text:line-break/> Pn n-o rmnea nic.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Venii cu toii dinpreun</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Venii cu toii din preun,<text:line-break/> S ne veselim,<text:line-break/> Cu toi acum i totdaun,<text:line-break/> Vinul s-l jertvim.<text:line-break/> i mari, i mici cu toi frete,<text:line-break/> S ne osptm,<text:line-break/> Cci bnd vinul veselete,<text:line-break/> i de griji uitm.<text:line-break/> Atunci mhnire nu este,</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cnd bem mai mult vin</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">Cnd bem mai mult vin,<text:line-break/> Brbai copii, i neveste,<text:line-break/> Toi veseli deplin.<text:line-break/> Toi cntnd ntru unpre,<text:line-break/> Toi s glsuim,<text:line-break/> Dnd la phar mulmire,<text:line-break/> Ndat s-l golim.<text:line-break/> Urmnd unul dup altul,<text:line-break/> Toi de rnd s bem,<text:line-break/> Fiecare cu tot artul,<text:line-break/> Bei s ne vedem.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3"><text:soft-page-break/>O! Veselie la mas</text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3">O! Veselie la mas,<text:line-break/> O! Ce beie aleas.<text:line-break/> O frumoas adunare,<text:line-break/> Tot de carii scurg phare.<text:line-break/> O! Ce vin nvoire,<text:line-break/> C toi au gust de sorbire,<text:line-break/> Tot de carii vin le place,<text:line-break/> i cup n-au a face.<text:line-break/> Hai dar toi c-o glsuire,<text:line-break/> Cu chiot ntr-o unire.<text:line-break/> S-n nlm phare pline,<text:line-break/> i s le scurgem toi bine.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P3"/>
   <text:p text:style-name="P15">SFRIT.<text:line-break/> TOMULU NTIU.</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="P34" text:outline-level="1">Fabule i istorioare </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Subtitle">(1841)</text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Copaciul i dovleacul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pe lng un copaci mare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Un dovleac, din ntmplare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Primvara rsrise</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i pe dnsul s suise,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Care ntr-att crescuse,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">nct vrfu-i ntrecuse,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">n lung i-n lat s-ntinsese,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ramurile-i cuprinsese,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i pretutindeni umpluse</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">De dovleci care fcuse.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deci cu aceast iestime</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vzndu-se la nlime,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">ncepu s se mndreasc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i zicnd s se fleasc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vezi, eu numa-ntr-o var</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ct crescui i tot cresc iar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i tu copaci din vechime,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">n sum de ani mulime,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">D-ai fi crescut voinicete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Precum i vrejul meu crete,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mai, mai ajungeai la stele,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dup prelele mele.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Iar copaciul cel cu minte</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">I-a rspuns aste cuvinte:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ei! te lauzi tu acuma,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">C nc n-ai vzut bruma,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar cnd va da i zpad,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Atuncea eti jos grmad!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vzndu-te la nlime,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gndete la viitoare</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i la cele-ntmpltoare.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nu te nla cu firea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pn&apos; nu cerci nenorocirea.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Lupul, pocit </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="Epigraph">Lupul prul i leapd,<text:line-break/>dar nravul nu-i las<text:line-break/> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Un lup dac-a-mbtrnit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">ntr-o zi ce i-a venit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">A vrut a s poci</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i faptele a-i ci.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deci cu acest al su gnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Numele-n cine schimbnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S-a smerit ca un btrn</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i s-a bgat la stpn,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S slujeasc ntr-un an</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">La oi, pe lng cioban.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">ntr-acest chip dar slujind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i oile-n cmp pznd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">ntr-o zi fiind lungit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">O oaie l-a mirosit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">El ndat -a uitat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C e n, cine schimbat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-apucnd oaia de trup</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">O jertvi-n grab ca un lup.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ciobanul peste el dnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-aceast fapt vznd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Ce-ai fcut, l-a ntrebat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cine btrn i spurcat?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Iar el smerit s uita</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-ntr-acest chip s-ndrepta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Eu, zise, fiind culcat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">M-apucasem de visat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Oaia cum ptea-mprejur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vind tocma ca un fur,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pe la pate m muca</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i coada mi mbuca.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Eu i-am zis o dat mr,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">I-am zis -alt dat br</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar ea tot m supra</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i nu s astmpra.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Atunci i eu, necjit,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Cum o trntii, a murit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i de fric s n-o vezi</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i s m-nvinovezi,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Apucai de o mncai.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i n burt o bgai.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar ciobanul nu glmni,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dndu- una-l adormi.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Cltorul i stejarul </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Un cltor ostenind.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i la un stejar sosind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Subt umbra lui a ezut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S rsufle un minut.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aci un bostan fiind</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i n el pepeni zrind,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Mergnd, unul a luat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i supt copaci l-a mncat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deci ochii-n sus ardicnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Gndea-ntru sine zicnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ce lucru nepotrivit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dumnezeu a rnduit!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C la un copaci asfel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S fac rod mititel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Iar la un vrej slab pe jos,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aa rod mare i gros!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pe cnd aceste gndea</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i cu ochii-n sus privea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">O ghind s-a slobozit</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i toma-n nas l-a izbit.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Atunci el nasul suflnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Zise iar ntr-al su gnd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ce nesocotit snt eu!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bine-a fcut Dumnezeu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar de nu era rod mic</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-era pepene, cum zic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aa-n cap de m lovea,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Aci-n loc m adormea.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Iar de era vrun dovleac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Apoi nu-mi mai dam de leac.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P10"><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Multe un fel s gndesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i altfel s potrivesc.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">D-unde tii c sunt hagiu? </text:h>
   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Odat un negustor</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Fiind pe drum cltor,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Patru hoi l ntlnesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">l dezbrac, l jefuiesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i ntr-un minut de ceas</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Numa-n cma l las.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dup ce l-au dezbrcat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unul din ei s-a uitat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i cmaa nou vznd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Striga celorlali zicnd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Nici cmaa nu-i lsai</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">i de dnsa-l dezbrcai!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Iar bietul om striga:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Jupn hagiu! f-mi st dar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Las-mi cmaa mcar.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Houl auzind astfel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S-a rstit privind la el:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Spune-mi c nu te las viu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">D-unde cunoti c sunt hagiu?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Omul rspunse pe loc:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Ba nu te cunosc deloc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dect jupnelul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Auz de la alii i eu</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">C hagii aa fac,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Adic: de tot dezbrac</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T5"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T1">Houl rznd l-a iertat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i lsndu-l a plecat.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:h text:style-name="Heading_20_3" text:outline-level="3">Ceretorii cltori </text:h>
