teti.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">El prin ei cum s-a uitat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">A zis: -Geab mi le-ai dat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C nu poci citi de loc;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S vede c n-am noroc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Boltaul, privind la el,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">I-a zis: -Eu mai am un fel</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i crez c-o s poi cu ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar snt prea scumpi i nu iei.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">El zise: -Adu-i ncoci,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">F&apos;e scumpi numai s poci.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dac i-a dat, a zis iar:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-i cu aceti n zdar,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C, uite, ochii-mi bleojdesc</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i tot nu poci s citesc.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Of! i ce poft aveam,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Acas cnd m gndeam!</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vnztorui l-a-ntrebat:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Cum te vz, n-ai nvat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i acum te cznesti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Pentru nti s citeti?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Vezi bine a rspuns el,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">D-aceea venii c-un miel,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C d-a ti eu s citesc,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:s