   <text:p text:style-name="P21"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unul avnd un nepot</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Srac i lipsit de tot,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Vine ntr-o zi la el</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i s roag-ntr-acest fel:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Unchiule, bine m ti</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C n-am coprins, nici moii,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Bani nu mi-a dat Dumnezeu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S negustoresc i eu.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">La multe m cam pricep,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar n-am cu ce s ncep,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ndejdi a m-ajuta</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">N-am dect la dumneata;</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">De aceea, unchiul meu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">M rog ca la Dumnezeu,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">S-mi dai cinci sute de lei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ca s fac nego cu ei,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-n jumtate de an</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-i rspunz pn&apos;la un ban.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unchiul su s-a ndurat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">La vorba ce l-a rugat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i mna sa ardicnd</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i arat sus, zicnd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Vezi acea oal din cui?</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1"