>Ca i ali sraci cum cer.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Unchiul su cel nelat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i d-al doilea rugat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">N-a zis nimic, a tcut,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C-a uitat s-a prefcut</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i, iar spre cui cutnd,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Arat oala, zicnd:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Acolo orci gseti,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ia-i i s negustoreti.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nepotul iar bucuros</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">A dat oala pe loc jos.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Dar dac a cutat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Nimic n ea n-a aflat.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i cu prere de ru .</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">A zis ctre unchiul su:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Unchiule, iar o ardic,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">C nu e n ea nimic.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Deci unchiul su n-a ascuns,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ci-l dete acest rspuns:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">-Apoi de cnd ai luat</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">ntr-nsa ai mai bgat,</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">i ai venit iar s cei</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">Ca s gseti i s iei?.</text:span></text:p>
